<!-- > ##### Variant Rule: On a Pale Horse
> GMs might consider making the creatures summoned by a death knight with *find steed* and *find greater steed* undead, rather than one of the creature types listed in those spells.

> ##### Variant Rule: Xorothian Steed
> GMs might prefer making the creatures summoned by a warlock with the *find steed* and *find greater steed* fiends instead of the other creature types listed in those spells. Additionally, the *find greater steed* spell can summon a felsteed in addition to the other creatures listed. -->

