### Spell List Changes
#### Additions
- **Death Knights:** Animate Crawling Claw, Arctic Breath, Bad Blood, Cold Snap, *Cloudkill*, Consumptive Field, Crippling Agony, Entomb, Flash Freeze, Ghastly Stench, Nauseating Poison, Poison Dart, Poison Puff, Spider Bite, Stinging Swarm, *Stinking Cloud*, Vicious Vapors
- **Druids:** *Cloudkill*, *Infestation*, Nauseating Poison, Poison Puff, *Poison Spray*, Rain of Spiders, Spider Bite, Stardust, *Stinking Cloud*, Sunfire/Moonfire, Vicious Vapors
- **Mages:** Arcane Bolt, Arcane Lance, Arcane Orb, Arcane Storm, Arctic Breath, Cold Snap, Conjure Servant, Create Mana Gem, Entomb, Flash Freeze, Force Blade, Prismatic Spray
- **Paladins:** Aura of Faith, Avenger's Smite
- **Priests:** Aura of Faith
- **Shamans:** Aero Barrage, Become Fire, Become Stone, Become Water, Become Wind, Crackle, Crashing Wave, Create Effigy, Dancing Wave, Electric Smite, Electrocute, *Fire Storm*, Fissure, Form of Fire, Form of Ice, Form of Stone, Form of the Elements, Form of Water, Form of Wind, Gale Bolt, Geyser, Hurricane Slash, Jumping Jolt, Orbital Stones, Pressure Cutter, Rain of Frogs, *Ray of Frost*, Sky Burst, Spiritual Consultation, Stone Fist, Thundercrack, Thunder Pulse, Thunder Punch, Tornado, Vortex Blast, Water Blast, Water Cannon, Windborne Weapon
